  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This role is responsible of testing the application for key security vulnerabilities at the unit/component level.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <keyConsiderations>The person in this role will work with other security specialists to understand and fix the more complex security issues.</keyConsiderations>
  <skills>&lt;p>&#xD;
    A person&amp;nbsp;filling this role should have the following skills:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Basic understanding&amp;nbsp;of testing approaches and techniques at the unit or component level, or both&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Basic understanding of Web application security&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Training in secure coding&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Debugging and diagnostic skills in the security domain&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Good knowledge of the component being tested&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Training in the use of security test automated tools&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Experience using the security test automated tools&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></skills>
